{"thag2.47:0.1":"Theragatha 2.47 ","thag2.47:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.47:0.3":"Pancamavagga ","thag2.47:0.4":"Anupamattheragatha ","thag2.47:1.1":"“Nandamanagatam cittam, ","thag2.47:1.2":"sulamaropamanakam; ","thag2.47:1.3":"Tena teneva vajasi, ","thag2.47:1.4":"yena sulam kalingaram. ","thag2.47:2.1":"Taham cittakalim brumi, ","thag2.47:2.2":"tam brumi cittadubbhakam; ","thag2.47:2.3":"Sattha te dullabho laddho, ","thag2.47:2.4":"manatthe mam niyojayi”ti. ","thag2.47:2.5":"… Anupamo thero …. "}